{"tid":1481890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日 維園見 今晚 返屋企","createTime":"2019-08-18T01:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T05:04:05.000Z","uid":244636,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0059126b31a87758f5aa0f87d2b6400a356034aa","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:45:36.000Z","msg":"兩點 入維園 入維園好多人 離開維園好多人 <br />\n行到 我想行多兩個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞爆港島</span><br />\n唔好分化，勿捉鬼，企出黎既都係香港人！<br />\n<br />\n今晚 返屋企 和理非 + 勇武 Stand as ONE<br />\n用人數話比香港人知 話比大陸知 話比國際知<br />\n依場運動會繼續！！ 5大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n聽日新聞focus既點係人數人數人數<br />\n一大把兜把聲林鄭<br />\n<br />\n前線手足喺818只有一個目標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d04a088221459f224389410e0cf5f6d09afbbb","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XECcDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XECcDs.jpg&h=29389bc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8bd017ec276c1c030960a0bd3104a9bcf65f71","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PE6w1wV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPE6w1wV.jpg&h=7ea03432&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71120c37d32ca0f63df9f0afee238340b3443339","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJ5JSDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJ5JSDH.jpg&h=662f3eaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d872a5b8a6875c959620048c5d600eedd3b7248","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPxgtb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPxgtb9.jpg&h=4b42ddc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15cba472c3ed51cdd55dc871dda6df5473a76cbb","tid":1481890,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"陳雲：收到友人告知，共產黨鼓勵明日銅鑼灣維園集會的偽港獨派去衝擊解放軍軍營，幫共產黨製造鎮壓的藉口。共產黨也會假扮偽港獨做衝擊行動。<br />\n又是偽港獨派啊老友。今日的光復紅土行動，警察大概知道有共匪假扮示威者要打殺他們之後，知道共產黨要借警察的命一用，故此大致克制，催淚彈也沒放一個（旺角放了一個但不肯定）。明日就大概輪到偽港獨派盡地一煲，衝擊軍營，引誘黑武警來鎮壓。<br />\n參加維園流水集會的泛民支持者也要小心，站一下、報個名就馬上走，不要滯留，以免被殃及池魚。即使是泛民的支持者，我也勸他們小心，局面凶險，邊境集結的幾萬福建武警，每日在燒共產黨的錢，是等待機會動用的。"},{"pid":"b9c24573cd97b3a0a4bff244133b8606d0ad81fc","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gFFaqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gFFaqC.jpg&h=bcf26f40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5647ac68975d035b78b71ba2aa6058f0937205fa","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GThgtcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGThgtcz.jpg&h=48943898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4053cbb57bc973d444a603e0dd24b1849426ed7","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvZVJL1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvZVJL1.png&h=195d8e3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24c4090fd8fd6b544575cdfe0bd30c957a1af6f9","tid":1481890,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src